Job description 46 : 

Experience: 6-8 years.

- Salesforce DevOps Engineer responsible for implementing scalable solutions including continuous delivery, optimization, monitoring, release management and support the end to end release process.
- Have min 3+ years experience in Salesforce implementation - Sales Cloud/Service Cloud/Experience Cloud.
- Have min 2+ years hands-on experience in setting up CI/CD pipelines using any of the DevOps tools - Jenkins/AutoRabit/Azure DevOps.
- Have hands-on experience in setting up source control (GitHub) and release management.
- knowledge of 2nd generation managed packages and unlocked packages is a plus.
- Experience with Salesforce platform sandbox and scratch org deployments working in an agile methodology environment
- Experience working with overlapping product release cycles.
- Able to create/maintain release and procedure documents
- A good team player, ability to learn quickly, excellent written and spoken communication.

